ions division", "buckeye valley news and continuation of the buckeye review (buckeye, maricopa county, ariz.) 1935-1935", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 71.90378, "shelf_id": "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn97060136", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd"], "subject": ["arizona", "maricopa county", "maricopa", "united states", "buckeye", "maricopa county (ariz.)", "buckeye (ariz.)", "newspapers"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:38:22.884Z", "title": "Buckeye Valley news and continuation of the Buckeye review", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn97060136/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271093/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1955", "dates": ["[1955 TO 1965]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with volume III, number 1 (July 14, 1955); ceased with vol. XIII, no. 26 (February 3, 1965). Merged with: Westside citizen, to form: Westsider (Goodyear, Ariz.). Volume III, Number 1 (July 14, 1955); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed April 21, 2024). Vol. XII, Number 23 (December 19, 1963) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed April 21, 2024). Westside citizen Westsider (Goodyear, Ariz.)"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:15Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271093/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["arizona", "tolleson", "maricopa", "maricopa county", "united states", "phoenix", "litchfield park", "goodyear"], "number": ["2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2997-4690", "1430728187", "2024271093", "online resource"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Westside"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "westside enterprise (goodyear, arizona) 1955-1965 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 45.545025